Investor Overview
Accelerize Corporate Profile
Accelerize Inc. offers technology solutions that drive how advertisers leverage their data in new and innovative ways. Through its digital marketing software divison, CAKE, Accelerize offers a multi-channel marketing hub that enables marketers to accurately track, attribute and optimize digital spend across the entire customer journey.
 
